                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 839.51/960.</note>
                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Santo Domingo</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1913-02-23">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 23, 1913</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The contract was signed yesterday and awaits my endorsement. Will the change
                    mentioned in your February 19 necessitate a new contract, or can I, subject to
                    changes you make, endorse the present contract?</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Russell</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
